<h2>
    <a href="/blog/making-word-wheels/">Making word wheels</a>
</h2>




<h6 class="post-meta">
    Posted by:
    
    <a href="/blog/author/christian/">christian</a>
    
    
    
    
    on 31 Mar 2017
</h6>





<a href="/blog/making-word-wheels/">
    <img class="img-thumbnail pull-left" src="/static/media/uploads/blog/trie_anagram/.thumbnails/word_wheel_example2.png/word_wheel_example2-90x90.png">
</a>





<p>Just a small script to generate word wheel puzzles: run from the command line by giving the any number of letters (central letter first) and redirecting its output to a file. Output is as an SVG file.</p>




